Intro:
You enter a dangerous asteroid belt.
You try to escape it but the gravity of planets force you to go right into it.
When coming closer, you see that it's millions of oranges.

Choices:
* Bring out a net -> game: fruit ninja
* Run straight through, hot enough to melt the oranges -> game: asteroids

Endings
Fruit ninja
fail: The net fills with oranges and brings the whole ship to crash with the planet
win: 1000 Oranges in food storage+++

Asteroids
fail: Engine breaks and we are now floating without control silently in space
win: The ship gets an orange coating making it look golden and smell nice
